---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  pageKey="about"
  title="Austin Copps — Generative-AI builder, Dallas, TX"
  description="Hey, I'm Austin — a generative-AI builder in Dallas. I work on agentic AI at Worlds and ship full-stack products outside of that. Glad you're here."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative pt-4 md:pt-10 pb-20 md:pb-28">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <!-- Left signal column — light, simple -->
      <aside class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-5 md:pt-3">
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-coral">
          <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-coral rounded-full mr-2 align-middle animate-pulse"></span>
          Open to new work
        </p>
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500 leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
          Dallas, TX<br />Generative-AI builder
        </p>
      </aside>

      <!-- Headline column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-9">
        <h1
          class="reveal font-display font-light text-fluid-display text-cream-900 leading-[0.92] tracking-tightest"
          style="transition-delay: 60ms;"
        >
          Hi, I'm Austin.<br />
          <span class="italic font-normal text-coral">I build things</span><br />
          with AI.
        </h1>

        <div class="reveal mt-10 md:mt-14 max-w-[58ch] text-fluid-lg text-cream-800 leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 220ms;">
          <p>
            I'm a Lead AI Analyst on the forward-deployed engineering team at
            <a class="link text-cream-900" href="https://worlds.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Worlds</a>.
            Outside of work I design, build, and maintain full-stack applications — a contracted classifier for a Dallas appellate court, a recommendation system for a recently-merged periodontics company, and a camp-safety platform launching on the App Store.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 md:gap-8" style="transition-delay: 320ms;">
          <a class="link font-mono text-mono-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-cream-900" href="/work">
            Work history&nbsp;&nbsp;→
          </a>
          <a class="link font-mono text-mono-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-cream-900" href="/projects">
            Projects&nbsp;&nbsp;→
          </a>
          <a
            class="link font-mono text-mono-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-cream-900"
            href="mailto:austin@austincopps.com"
          >
            Say hello&nbsp;&nbsp;→
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT — portrait + warm narrative -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-cream-200" id="about">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-y-12 md:gap-x-14 items-start">
      <!-- Portrait -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 lg:col-span-4">
        <figure class="reveal relative">
          <div class="relative bg-cream-50 p-3 border border-cream-200 shadow-[0_30px_60px_-30px_rgba(89,60,30,0.18)]">
            <img
              src="/portrait.jpg"
              alt="Austin Copps"
              width="1024"
              height="1024"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="block w-full h-auto select-none"
            />
          </div>
          <figcaption class="mt-3 font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500">
            Austin&nbsp;Copps&nbsp;·&nbsp;Dallas,&nbsp;TX
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <!-- Narrative -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 lg:col-span-8">
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-coral">A little about me</p>
        <h2
          class="reveal mt-4 font-display font-light text-fluid-3xl tracking-tightest text-cream-900 leading-[0.98] max-w-[18ch]"
          style="transition-delay: 80ms;"
        >
          I love<br />
          <span class="italic">building things.</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="reveal mt-10 max-w-readable text-fluid-base text-cream-800 leading-relaxed space-y-5" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
          <p>
            I'm a generative-AI builder based in Dallas, Texas. By day I'm the Lead AI Analyst at Worlds, working alongside a forward-deployed engineering team on production AI systems for industrial customers. I get a lot of energy out of sitting with the people who'll actually use the thing and figuring out how to make their day easier.
          </p>
          <p>
            Outside of work I keep building — full-stack apps, agentic systems, small experiments, and occasionally something that turns into a real product. I love collaborating with people who care about the craft.
          </p>
          <p>
            Above all of that, I love building things, fixing things, and solving problems. That's been the through-line my whole life.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Off-the-clock — friendly one-liner, no forced analogies -->
        <p class="reveal mt-12 max-w-readable text-fluid-base text-cream-700 leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 240ms;">
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500 block mb-2">Off the clock</span>
          Gaming, collecting cards, working on cars, building custom PCs, and getting out on the pickleball, tennis, and baseball courts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CURRENTLY — slim -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 border-t border-cream-200">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-coral">Currently</p>
        <h2 class="reveal mt-3 font-display font-light text-fluid-xl tracking-tightest text-cream-900">
          What I'm up to.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="md:col-span-8 flex flex-col">
        <li class="reveal grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-baseline border-t border-cream-200 py-5">
          <span class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-3 font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500">
            At work
          </span>
          <p class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-9 text-fluid-base text-cream-800 leading-relaxed">
            Leading the AI Analyst function at <span class="text-cream-900">Worlds</span>, supporting the full production and pilot AI portfolio on a forward-deployed team.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="reveal grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-baseline border-t border-cream-200 py-5" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
          <span class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-3 font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500">
            Shipping
          </span>
          <p class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-9 text-fluid-base text-cream-800 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="text-cream-900">Chirp</span>, my camp-safety platform, to the iOS and Android stores any day now.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="reveal grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-baseline border-t border-b border-cream-200 py-5" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
          <span class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-3 font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500">
            Tinkering
          </span>
          <p class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-9 text-fluid-base text-cream-800 leading-relaxed">
            Always-on agents, smarter retrieval, and a few small side-experiments that may or may not turn into something.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- REACH OUT -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-cream-200">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-7">
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-coral">Say hello</p>
        <h2 class="reveal mt-4 font-display font-light text-fluid-3xl tracking-tightest text-cream-900 leading-[0.95]">
          Let's <span class="italic">build something.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="reveal mt-6 max-w-readable text-fluid-lg text-cream-800 leading-relaxed">
          I'm always happy to chat — whether it's a role, a project, an interesting problem, or just to swap notes on AI. Drop a line.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-4 md:pt-6">
        <a class="reveal link group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 border-t border-cream-200 pt-5" href="mailto:austin@austincopps.com">
          <span class="font-display font-light text-fluid-lg text-cream-900">austin@austincopps.com</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">email</span>
        </a>
        <a class="reveal link group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 border-t border-cream-200 pt-5" href="tel:+14696629792" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
          <span class="font-display font-light text-fluid-lg text-cream-900">(469) 662-9792</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">phone</span>
        </a>
        <a class="reveal link group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 border-t border-cream-200 pt-5" href="https://linkedin.com/in/austin-copps-06332621b" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
          <span class="font-display font-light text-fluid-lg text-cream-900">/in/austin-copps</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">linkedin</span>
        </a>
        <a class="reveal link group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 border-t border-cream-200 pt-5" href="https://github.com/acopps1999" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="transition-delay: 240ms;">
          <span class="font-display font-light text-fluid-lg text-cream-900">@acopps1999</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cream-500 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">github</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
